intro: This game rolls roguelite and run and gunner into a tight experience with 1-4 couch co-op.
description:
Help Zealot find her lost brother, Solitude, in the vibrant but chaotic 'Other Dimension' where riches are abundant and dangers aplenty! 
 Combine bullet powers found on the field to create unique bullet types. Dash to avoid attacks but also to crash enemies or deflect bullets. 
Fight through randomised levels, challenge large bullet hell-like bosses and collect Red Eye Orbs to spend between attempts to permanently upgrade your abilities to help tip the tide and assist you in beating the game.
